99, in the singles draw!)\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3594, \"end\": 3603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.862403588941505e-19, \"text\": \"Amsterdam\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\"}, {\"begin\": 3614, \"end\": 3625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robin_Haase\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Robin Haase\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robin_Haase\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robin_Haase\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3571}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 3575, \"to\": 3582}, {\"ngram\": \"a double-take\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3650}, {\"ngram\": \"the singles\", \"from\": 3679, \"to\": 3690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But what choice is there?\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what choice\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have lucky losers at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lucky losers\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3753}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And sure, some top players took passes.\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some top players\", \"from\": 3782, \"to\": 3798}, {\"ngram\": \"passes\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But notthatmany.\", \"from\": 3812, \"to\": 3828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"But notthatmany\", \"from\": 3812, \"to\": 3827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(And I suspect there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s some FOMO from those who were eligible and passed.)\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some FOMO\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More on this below.\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 3925, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And an overall team event doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t really work for, say, Iga Swiatek or Djokovic.\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 4009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3985, \"end\": 3988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2193321927587014e-23, \"text\": \"Iga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\"}, {\"begin\": 4000, \"end\": 4008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3799627102582158e-27, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an overall team event\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 3952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Should they be denied when there are no Polish men and Serbian women, respectively, in the field?\", \"from\": 4010, \"to\": 4107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4050, \"end\": 4056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polish_language\", \"score\": 0.9627246164498824, \"rank\": 0.03863817743002702, \"text\": \"Polish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4065, \"end\": 4072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.8995641827219448, \"rank\": 0.1007371387449049, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like many of you, I wish it were prioritized by broadcast decision-makers.\", \"from\": 4109, \"to\": 4183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"broadcast decision-makers\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m all-in on Olympic tennis.\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"But I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4193}, {\"ngram\": \"all-in\", \"from\": 4194, \"to\": 4200}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic tennis\", \"from\": 4204, \"to\": 4218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And suspect most fans are as well.\", \"from\": 4220, \"to\": 4254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most fans\", \"from\": 4232, \"to\": 4241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If [Djokovic] had beaten Nadal 6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00931 6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00930 he would have been roundly criticized as an ass.\", \"from\": 4256, \"to\": 4347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Djokovic\", \"from\": 4260, \"to\": 4268}, {\"ngram\": \"6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00930\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4298}, {\"ngram\": \"an ass\", \"from\": 4340, \"to\": 4346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"J.B, Portland \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a2 Yes, probably from the social media mafia.\", \"from\": 4349, \"to\": 4410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"J.B\", \"from\": 4349, \"to\": 4352}, {\"ngram\": \"the social media mafia\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think most true/sane/sentient fans understand that A) few losing opponentswantcharity or mercy and B) especially with dangerous opponents\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and 22-time major winners at their venue of choice certainly meet this description\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094you cannot start handing out games.\", \"from\": 4411, \"to\": 4677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most true/sane/sentient fans\", \"from\": 4423, \"to\": 4451}, {\"ngram\": \"opponentswantcharity\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4502}, {\"ngram\": \"mercy\", \"from\": 4506, \"to\": 4511}, {\"ngram\": \"B\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4517}, {\"ngram\": \"dangerous opponents\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and 22-time major winners\", \"from\": 4535, \"to\": 4582}, {\"ngram\": \"their venue\", \"from\": 4586, \"to\": 4597}, {\"ngram\": \"choice\", \"from\": 4601, \"to\": 4607}, {\"ngram\": \"this description\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094you\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4645}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To be clear: Nadal won those additional games.\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4692, \"end\": 4697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.766024237297745e-26, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those additional games\", \"from\": 4702, \"to\": 4724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic gave no charity.\", \"from\": 4726, \"to\": 4751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Djokovic\", \"from\": 4726, \"to\": 4734}, {\"ngram\": \"no charity\", \"from\": 4740, \"to\": 4750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if he had closed it out 6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00931, 6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00930, he would simply have been doing his job.\", \"from\": 4752, \"to\": 4834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00931\", \"from\": 4780, \"to\": 4785}, {\"ngram\": \"6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00930\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4792}, {\"ngram\": \"his job\", \"from\": 4826, \"to\": 4833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And doing it well.\\u00c2 Hey Jon!\", \"from\": 4835, \"to\": 4864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 4853, \"to\": 4854}, {\"ngram\": \"Hey Jon\", \"from\": 4855, \"to\": 4862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two, tangentially related questions for you.\", \"from\": 4866, \"to\": 4910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tangentially related questions\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 4901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1) Do you think (or have you heard murmurings) that Swiatek\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s dominance on clay is one of the reasons for so many high-profile DNPs at the Olympics?\", \"from\": 4911, \"to\": 5061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"murmurings\", \"from\": 4946, \"to\": 4956}, {\"ngram\": \"Swiatek\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s dominance\", \"from\": 4963, \"to\": 4984}, {\"ngram\": \"clay\", \"from\": 4988, \"to\": 4992}, {\"ngram\": \"the reasons\", \"from\": 5003, \"to\": 5014}, {\"ngram\": \"so many high-profile DNPs\", \"from\": 5019, \"to\": 5044}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5048, \"to\": 5060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a subtle difference to me between Ben Shelton preparing for hardcourt, rightly feeling that clay doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t suit him best, and someone like [Aryna] Sabalenka\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094one of the best players in the world, who maybe feels like she should get ready for the Open instead of a playing a tournament where could AT BEST get the silver medal.\\u00c2 2) Speaking of medals, at what point do you think most players would value an Olympic victory over a slam?\", \"from\": 5062, \"to\": 5508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5106, \"end\": 5117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Shelton\", \"score\": 0.9999837952540147, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ben Shelton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Shelton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Shelton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a subtle difference\", \"from\": 5062, \"to\": 5091}, {\"ngram\": \"hardcourt\", \"from\": 5132, \"to\": 5141}, {\"ngram\": \"that clay doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t suit\", \"from\": 5159, \"to\": 5183}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 5198, \"to\": 5205}, {\"ngram\": \"the best players\", \"from\": 5238, \"to\": 5254}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5258, \"to\": 5267}, {\"ngram\": \"the Open\", \"from\": 5315, \"to\": 5323}, {\"ngram\": \"a tournament\", \"from\": 5345, \"to\": 5357}, {\"ngram\": \"AT BEST\", \"from\": 5370, \"to\": 5377}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver medal\", \"from\": 5382, \"to\": 5398}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 5399, \"to\": 5400}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 5416, \"to\": 5422}, {\"ngram\": \"what point\", \"from\": 5427, \"to\": 5437}, {\"ngram\": \"most players\", \"from\": 5451, \"to\": 5463}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic victory\", \"from\": 5476, \"to\": 5494}, {\"ngram\": \"a slam\", \"from\": 5500, \"to\": 5506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I assume the vast majority of players would much rather bag a major than get gold at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 5509, \"to\": 5607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vast majority\", \"from\": 5518, \"to\": 5535}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 5539, \"to\": 5546}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 5586, \"to\": 5590}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5594, \"to\": 5606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel that MOST players would rather sayI made the finals of a majorthan get silver.\", \"from\": 5608, \"to\": 5693, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"MOST players\", \"from\": 5620, \"to\": 5632}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5666}, {\"ngram\": \"a majorthan\", \"from\": 5670, \"to\": 5681}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 5686, \"to\": 5692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But how might they compare making a slam semifinal to winning the bronze?\", \"from\": 5694, \"to\": 5767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a slam\", \"from\": 5728, \"to\": 5734}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 5756, \"to\": 5766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"-n from California \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a2 I think the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Olympic field is quite strong and quite logical\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094as an athlete from Belarus, Sabalenka\\u00e2\\u